00:24:56,075 --> 00:24:57,258
You recognized it.

563
00:24:57,975 --> 00:24:59,625
You’re the first one

564
00:24:59,625 --> 00:25:01,375
to notice my special design tonight.

565
00:25:01,791 --> 00:25:02,583
I am?

566
00:25:02,958 --> 00:25:04,291
