the surface part.

573
00:25:19,750 --> 00:25:21,583
I didn’t expect you to know so much

574
00:25:21,583 --> 00:25:22,666
about design styles.

575
00:25:23,225 --> 00:25:24,650
That’s rare.

576
00:25:27,125 --> 00:25:29,625
