in front of you.

577
00:25:30,583 --> 00:25:31,800
After I give a speech,

578
00:25:32,416 --> 00:25:35,375
may I have a word

579
00:25:35,833 --> 00:25:37,041
with you?

580
00:25:37,375 --> 00:25:39,425
