667
00:30:48,958 --> 00:30:50,250
I’d certainly come to your party.

668
00:30:52,833 --> 00:30:55,541
Miss Gu, why do you have this necklace?

669
00:30:57,833 --> 00:30:58,833
I gave it to her.

670
00:30:59,458 --> 00:31:00,458
Last year in Spain,

671
00:31:00,791 --> 00:31:02,791
